==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|punischen}}, from {{etyl|xno|en}}, {{etyl|fro|en}} ''puniss-'', stem of some of the conjugated forms of {{m|fro|punir}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|punio|puniō, punīre|to inflict punishment upon}}, from {{m|la|poena||punishment, penalty}}; see {{m|en|pain}}.

